title: Juliana Hatfield Type Stuffs
description:
Here we have 12 albums worth of Juliana Hatfields work (including a couple Blake Babies albums and Some Girls, missing Juliana&#039;s Pony-Total System Failure), most ripped from my personal collection using EAC, Lame Encoder at a high variable bit rate. The only album not ripped by me but included is the never released God&#039;s Foot album that was to come out around 1996. The albums included in this torrent are:

Blake Babies - Innocence and Experience (1993)
Juliana Hatfield - Hey Babe (1992)
The Juliana Hatfield Three - Become What You Are (1993)
Juliana Hatfield - Only Everything (1995)
Juliana Hatfield - God&#039;s Foot (unreleased)
Juliana Hatfield - Bed (1998)
Juliana Hatfield - Beautiful Creature (2000)
Blake Babies - God Bless the Blake Babies (2001)
Juliana Hatfield - Gold Stars:1992-2002 (2002 - a best of album)
Some Girls - Feel It (2003)
Juliana Hatfield - In Exile Deo (2004)
Juliana Hatfield - Made In China (2005)
